description:
ExpertPdf Html To Pdf Converter is a .NET library that can be used in any .NET application to offer support for converting web pages to pdf documents.

ExpertPdf HtmlToPdf Converter has full support for HTML5, CSS3, web fonts, modern javascript.

ExpertPdf does not have any external dependencies. It works on any .NET platform, starting with .NET 2.0 and on any Windows operating system (32bit or 64bit) starting with Windows XP.
releaseNotes:
New features in v9.2.0:

- Possibility to start the conversion by calling a javascript method (set pdfConverter.StartupMode = StartupMode.Manual in .NET and call ExpertPdfJSObj.startConversion(); in javascript).

- Javascript injection (use pdfConverter.StartupScript to set some javascript code that will run at startup, before any other script on the page).

- Possibility to use @media print CSS styles for conversion instead of the default @media screen (set pdfConverter.UsePrintCSSMediaType = true).
summary: ExpertPdf HtmlToPdf offers the possibility to convert html to pdf in any .NET application.
title: ExpertPdf Html To Pdf Converter
